d6 die based system

AC
Based on speed rank (meets it beats it)
S - 21
A - 17
B - 14
C - 10
D - 7
E - 3

When close range stands do a western shoot out kind of deal they will roll speed before each bought

Hit Points
a rolled amount
S - 20/21
A - 18/19
B - 16/17
C - 14/15
D - 12/13
E - 10/11

To Hit
Roll precision

Crits
if all die crit you can roll the dice again and add the new value rolled to the initial number

Wounds
  -Wounds are taken after a stands defenses have been breached
1. shaken
2. incapacitated or deaths door


refernce for stand user stats

Power - C
Speed - C
Range - C
Durability - C
Precision - C
Potential -C


